    "description": "竹子製作器物的淵源很早，最早是出現在春秋戰國時候的楚國，而台灣竹編工藝的技術，隨著時代的改變與進步，已融入各種新材料，嶄現新風貌。本課程旨在為了讓學生學習傳統工藝竹編藝術，並融合創意巧思，為傳統注入新生命",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.竹編的歷史與發展<br>2.認識竹材<br>3.基本竹編法--平面壓一編織法<br>4.基本竹編法--平面壓二編織法<br>5.基本竹編法--平面壓三編織法<br>6.米字型打底法（基本編織法）<br>7.斜編、直編、盤纏編<br>8.六角目的變化<br>9.竹編飾品<br>10.竹編扇自行創作<br>11.竹藝品的上漆與保存方法<br>12.作品的防潮處理",
        "en": "1. History and development of bamboo knitting<br>2. Know bamboo<br>3. Basic Bamboo Weaving Method--Plane Pressing and Weaving Method<br>4. Basic Bamboo Weaving Method--Plane Pressing Two Weaving Method<br>5. Basic Bamboo Weaving Method--Plane Pressing Three Weaving Method<br>6. Meter type base method (basic weaving method)<br>7. Diagonal, straight, and entangled<br>8. Hexagonal purpose changes<br>9. Bamboo ornaments<br>10. Bamboo fan made by himself<br>11. Painting and preservation methods of bamboo art<br>12. Moisture treatment of the work"
